million gallons of water for San Clemente and other Tri-Cities Municipal Water 
District customers. Gomez is a district supervisor. TONY / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, (A2) Above, Tri-Cities Municipal Water District supervisor Tony E. Gomez 
at the 48-million-gallon Palisades Reservoir. DON KELSEN / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
