the Orange County Performing Arts Center Triathlon leaves the starting line to 
begin the 1.5-kilometer swim competition Sunday. ROD BOREN / For The Times; 
Photo, Colleen Cannon, 1988 winner, held off Karen Smyer to win the women's 
division of Orange County Performing Arts Center triathlon. ROD BOREN / For The 
Times 
</P>
