<DOCID> 228842 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 4, 1990, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 5; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
