MORALITY; GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; POLITICAL CORRUPTION; LEGISLATION -- ALASKA; 
DEMOCRACY; EASTERN EUROPE -- GOVERNMENT; DOCUMENTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
